ly, we discuss a variant of the problem in which\nthe exchanges between adjacent particles happened at rates proportional to the\ndifference in their labels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 17 Mar 2019 15:03:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
